description: About 190 Manx and Guernsey people return home after flights between the two islands are suspended.
title: Isle of Man holidaymakers flown home following Guernsey air bridge suspension
title_page: Isle of Man holidaymakers flown home following Guernsey air bridge suspension - BBC News
maintext: One of the individuals had been in close contact with someone in the UK who had the virus, while the other two were found through the contact tracing process. All three are now in self-isolation.
